    	<h2><a name="2003-12-03" href="#2003-12-03"><font color="#660000">2003-12-03</font></a></h2>
   	

	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107049281515659860">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.acm.org/ubiquity/interviews/v4i40_ticoll.html">ACM: Ubiquity - The Dawning of the Age of Transparency</a>.&nbsp; A good read about a good read on Transparency.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107049281515659860">12/3/2003 03:06:55 PM</a></span></div>
<br>
